---
---

<section class="problem" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="fade-in">
      <span class="section-label">The Problem</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Finance apps are stuck in the past</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin: 0 auto 0;">They show you what already happened — never what's coming next.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-grid fade-in">
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Overdraft Surprises</h3>
        <p>You only discover you're short on funds after it's too late and the fees hit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/><line x1="8" y1="14" x2="8" y2="14.01"/><line x1="12" y1="14" x2="12" y2="14.01"/><line x1="16" y1="14" x2="16" y2="14.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Can't Plan Purchases</h3>
        <p>No way to know if you can afford that trip or gadget next month without guesswork.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/><path d="M20.49 15a9 9 0 1 1-2.12-9.36L23 10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Always Reactive</h3>
        <p>You're always looking in the rearview mirror, never through the windshield.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-block fade-in">
      <h3>The fix: <span class="gradient-text">predict, don't react</span></h3>
      <p>AnticiFi uses AI to analyze your spending patterns and predict your future balance — for any date you choose. Ask it in plain language, and know your financial future before it happens.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .problem .container {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .problem-card {
    padding: 32px 24px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .problem-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .problem-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .problem-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .solution-block {
    padding: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08));
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .solution-block h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .solution-block p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .solution-block { padding: 24px; }
  }
</style>
